Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:14.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我想打从心里大叫一句 好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:28.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我相信总有一天 一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}起步走出 希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:57.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:12.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:27.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}但愿你不会忘记最重要的事 永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快啊 下礼拜就要举行婚礼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们刚去给惣一郎扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,五代 响子就拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始可能会让她吃苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始过得勤俭节约一点 也比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎也可以安心长眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#96只要这份爱还在! 永远的一刻馆!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 就这样继续住在管理员室?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 搬家需要花一笔很大的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且音无家的爸爸 也已经答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以暂时会住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是精打细算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费是最大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么东西要烧的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有新婚的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是第二次结婚了 也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以丢掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,这个也麻烦你烧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一次结婚 拍的婚纱照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,不可以啦 怎么可以随便翻别人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要看,我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有新娘子的感觉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你看你看 管理员的婚纱照很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦 没有必要强迫他看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次看到 惣一郎的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是个很温柔的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有必要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不能把这些东西 放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是些结婚照而已 没有什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道一切事情 才决定结婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么会去在意这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子的心情 应该也早就整理好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惣一郎的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就会拿去还给音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好像很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,我并没有舍不得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我应该早点还给他们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必勉强还给他们也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要做个了断,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跟管理员吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就吵架 以后日子会很难过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有吵架啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那我去看“福星小子”的录影带好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后的日子…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再来一碗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我得出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我会去一趟音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归还遗物的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟惣一郎说一声才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来这里做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我很羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使将遗物归还音无家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想响子也绝对 不可能忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这不是忘不忘记的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早已经成为 响子心中的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我会继续努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到响子的时候 她心中就已经有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上的就是这样的响子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要连你一起,把响子娶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我能遇到这个人 你一定会为我感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你怎么来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要问你呢,幼稚园呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趁午休时间偷溜出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的遗物 等一下我要把它拿去还给爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你听我说 那个真的没必要勉强归还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够遇见你,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,爷爷,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是郁子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点都认不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公,快来 音无家的亲家公来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好久不见了 你变得好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母,不要糗我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是贤太郎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,你一点都没变耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,一直都长不高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法啊 都是妈妈的遗传
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶打扮好了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那五代哥哥呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张得半死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好帅的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得真早 结婚典礼还没开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向公司报外出溜出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也很仰慕管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很羡慕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子婶婶打扮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去看看,快去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是住在横须贺的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你还只有这么小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我们都不担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公,你也说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出来是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷,快来啊,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几年来 真的很感谢你的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我等这一天等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管去找你的幸福吧 连以前的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了今天 才来到这个世上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看,脸上的妆会花掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本日已被包下店长)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,椅子不够耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,欢迎新郎新娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜,恭喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-部长 -老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都来啦 谢谢你们,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那么大家来干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地上铺张报纸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,你来得正好 现在才要开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 因为我去了一趟医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生病了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,不要害羞了 快点进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子真的好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是双胞胎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话 我才要恭喜你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看起来很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,不要这样啦 太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么好丢脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么值得庆贺的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,你也来跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请新郎倌五代 为大家致辞答谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很感谢各位来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在终于可以 当一名称职的褓父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前发生过许多不如意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,从学生时代开始 当我痛苦难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏现在在场的各位亲友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严厉的指责或是鼓励我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在仍是个靠不住的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后说不定 还会给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟这里的响子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟响子两人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢各位 -谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,好舒服的风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好可以醒醒酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这身和服好不习惯 腰酸背痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是在饭店订了房间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜月旅行下午才出发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们想住在一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,我们回去慢慢喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然敲定了,就快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我回来了 -我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样,日子一天天过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里住习惯了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就适应这里的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我老公陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧姓七尾小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定居名古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫妻和睦,生活美满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰瞬,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生了一对双胞胎女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三胎也指日可待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去联谊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定可以认识帅哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神伊吹,正在念女子大学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是干嘛 你已经有认识帅哥了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神的心 好像还留在高中时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还无法忘记老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太专情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,你不是有太太了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经分居好几年 最近终于正式离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六本木朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住在茶茶丸的二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着,樱花的季节又到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,这是老板叫我带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员是今天出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,差不多就要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们两人 今后有什么打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们明明说 生了小孩之后就要搬离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是继续住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了,这样很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,让我看看小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸红通通的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟爸爸一样健康
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女孩吧,名字决定了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取作春天的香味,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,春香,真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香,我们回到家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈 第一次见面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在五号房 我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面,从今天起 我是这栋公寓的管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫音无响子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(相聚一刻全剧终)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:43.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:56.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:09.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情 亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:27.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你比我想像中冷淡 喜欢一个人独处 沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:38.40,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}不要逞强 在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:55.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}凝视着你的一切 试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.53,0:25:03.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:15.48,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}自我陶醉故弄玄虚 对我行不通…woo

